SHOPS

>> INFORMATION
You can buy or sell something in shop. Try "list", to see what is available.
And, you can only buy listed things, but can sell not listed things.
To sell, Each object to sell must be matched by object's type. (that is, you
can sell weapon in weapon shop, but can't do it in armor shop, and vice versa)

EXAMPLE :
	> sell sword
	> buy armor
	> list

See also : BUY, SELL, LIST
