very good idea to check it out once in a while.

See also : BOARD, WRITE, POST
#
BOARD

>> INFOMATION
If you find any bug or have something to tell to GOD, write on the board.

See also : NEWS, WRITE, POST
#
WRITE POST

>> COMMAND
To write on the board, you must have a paper and a pen.
If you have already those stuffs, first "write paper pen".
After, you can post written paper on the board in board room.
To post, type "post paper <title>".

See also : NEWS, BOARD
#
SLEEP WAKE REST SIT STAND

>> COMMAND
