>> SPELL : MAGIC USER, CLERIC, THIEF

USAGE        : cast 'poison' <victim | food | drink>
ACCUMULATIVE : Yes on persons.
DURATION     : level / 5 + 1 hours, or permanent on food and drinks.

Casting poison on food or drink (containers) will poison it.
Eating poisoned food/drinks will poison the person eating or drinking.

If victim saves para, poison can't be affected.
A person who is poisoned will suffer some points of damage every hour,
and gain less points than usual. And poisoned victim's strength is
reduced.

See also : REMOVE POISON
