DISINTERGRATE

>> SPELL : MAGIC USER

USAGE        : cast 'disintergrate' <victim>
ACCUMULATIVE : -
DURATION     : Instantaneous

This spell damage is propotional to caster's level and victim's level.
No affect by sanctuary. If victim saves spell damage will be less.
