QUEST

>> COMMAND
You can contact with QM(Quest Manager) by this command. If you are over 10
level, you should make quest to advance more level. QM proposes a quest to
you, and he will give some quest item, if you make it.

See also : REQUEST, HINT
#
REQUEST

>> COMMAND
If you can't make your quest proposed by QM, QM allows you to change your
quest by this command. But it gives you some penalties.

See alse : QUEST, HINT
#
HINT

>> COMMAND
QM gives some hint to your quest.

See also : QUEST, REQUEST
#
SKILLED

>> INFORMATION
Attribute of skills and spells has 2 fields - learned and skilled. They
mean How you learned and used the skill and the spell. The more SKILLED
field makes it's skill more powerful.

See also : BARE HAND
#
BARE HAND

>> INFORMATION
If you wield nothing, you will hit with your hand. If you are a warrior
and you use bare hand, the damage of your bare hand increases.

See also : SKILLED
